	<h1 class="tt">About</h1>
	
	<div class ="intro">

<p class = "para">Welcome to ProParts, where innovation meets automotive excellence! Our web application is your ultimate tool for seamless store maintenance and database management within the realm of spare parts. ProParts is designed to cater to a diverse user base, including customers, shop managers, warehouse heroes, suppliers, and our vigilant system administrators. Each role is equipped with specialized functions and features, ensuring a tailored experience for all.</p><br><p class = "para">

System administrators play a pivotal role, responsible for initiating the registration process. Unlike other users, admins can self-register due to the strict security protocols in place. They also have the exclusive authority to register other users and dispatch login credentials securely, whether by email or traditional mail. If incorrect credentials are provided, users have the opportunity to re-enter their details and try again.</p><br><p class = "para">

Shop managers take the reins of shop inventory management, allowing them to order items, keep inventory up-to-date, and generate comprehensive reports. Additionally, they have the capability to manage employees, from hiring to editing employee details and even handling terminations.</p><br><p class = "para">

Warehouse managers hold the key to inspecting and maintaining stock quality, efficient inventory management, and supplier relations. These experts can order items, update inventory, add new items, and process returns. Supplier management is another aspect under their control, which includes adding, editing, and removing supplier details.</p><br><p class = "para">

Warehouse employees are the backbone of our inventory, ensuring stock quality remains impeccable and handling the supply of orders to our shops. Suppliers play an equally crucial role, fulfilling orders and overseeing quality assurance and certification.</p><br><p class = "para">

Lastly, our revered system administrators oversee security, access control, shop management, database management, and data field edits. The ability to add, edit, or remove shops and maintain backups and recovery is also at their fingertips.</p><br><p class = "para"> 

At ProParts, we offer role-specific interfaces and functions for users, making it a versatile platform tailored to your needs. With this system, you gain access to a world of vehicle spare parts management, coupled with the convenience and efficiency you deserve.</p> <br> <p class = "para">

In conclusion, ProParts is your one-stop solution for monitoring and managing tasks encompassed within the realm of vehicle spare parts. Welcome to a new era of automotive excellence and database management!</p>


